transcript:
Customer: ویسے السلام علیکم
Agent: Walaikum assalam! Aapka kya haal hai? Aap bataiye main aapki kis madad mein madad kar sakta hoon?
Customer: مجھے اپنی بیلنس انکوئیری کرنی ہے
Agent: Bilkul, aap please apna account number bata dijiye taake main aapka balance check kar sakoon.
Agent: Nahi, aapko sirf apna account number dena hoga. PIN ki zaroorat nahi hai. Aapka account number milte hi main aapka balance foran check kar doonga.
Agent: Bilkul theek,
Agent: Aapko account
Customer: Gente, foi muito bom.
